<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Affiliate Program!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .code-block {
            background: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: monospace;
            word-break: break-all;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="<%= logoUrl || 'https://via.placeholder.com/150' %>" alt="<%= appName %>" class="logo">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Affiliate Program!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for joining the <strong><%= appName %></strong> Affiliate Program! We're excited to have you on board and can't wait to help you start earning commissions.</p>
        
        <h3>Your Affiliate Details:</h3>
        <p><strong>Referral Code:</strong></p>
        <div class="code-block"><%= referralCode %></div>
        
        <p><strong>Your Referral Link:</strong></p>
        <div class="code-block"><%= referralLink %></div>
        
        <p>Share your unique referral link with friends, family, and your audience to start earning commissions on every sale you refer!</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
            <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">Go to Your Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        
        <h3>How It Works:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Share your unique referral link or code</li>
            <li>Visitors click your link and make a purchase</li>
            <li>You earn a commission on every sale!</li>
        </ol>
        
        <p>You can track your referrals, commissions, and request payouts directly from your affiliate dashboard.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reply to this email or contact our support team at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a>.</p>
        
        <p>Happy selling!</p>
        <p>The <%= appName %> Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= currentYear %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You're receiving this email because you signed up for an account with <%= appName %>.</p>
        <p><a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/preferences">Update email preferences</a> | <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
